<FONT FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE="+1" CLASS="1" COLOR="#0102C6"><B>GAME INFO</B></FONT>
<BR>
<FONT FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE="3" CLASS="2" COLOR="#0000FE"><B>ALL THE INFO ON ROLLERCOASTER TYCOON</B></FONT><P>
<FONT FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE="-2" CLASS="text">
<P>
<FONT FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE="3" CLASS="3" COLOR="#0060FF"><B>NEW</B></FONT><BR>
<B>ADDED MARCH 15th 2000</B> - The thrid and final part in our feature on <A HREF="editing_room3.html">the Evolution of RollerCoaster Tycoon - Part 3</A> (aka The Editing Room Floor) has been released.  RollerCoaster Tycoon has loads of different rides, stalls, interfaces but what about all those items that didn't make it into the game?  Where do they all go?  Now, you can take a peek behind the scenes and see the elements you've never seen before.  You'll see how the game developed over it's development period.  We think some items will surprise you and some will even make you laugh.  <A HREF="editing_room1.html">Part 1</A> and <A HREF="editing_room2.html">part 2</A> are also available.
<P>

<FONT FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE="3" CLASS="3" COLOR="#0060FF"><B>ABOUT THE GAME</B></FONT><BR>
Get <A href="outline.html">the lowdown</A> on the game itself or <A HREF="official_add_on.html">the official add-on pack</A>.  Plus, see what the hype's about by viewing the magnificent <A href="screenshots.html">screenshots</A>.  Also, if you're not sure your PC is fast enough to run the game, then check the <A Href="tech.html">tech notes</A>.  Finally, don't take our word for it - read what others have been saying about
RollerCoaster Tycoon in our <a href="previews.html">review</A> section.
<P>

<FONT FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE="3" CLASS="3" COLOR="#0060FF"><B>INSIDE THE GAME</B></FONT><BR>
If you want to know more about the game's creation, read an <A href="interview.html">interview with Chris Sawyer</A>, the game designer.  Plus, you can read <a href="tips.html">Chris's top 10 tips</A> - specially written for the official Web site.  And, if that's not enough we've got a continually expanding <a href="faq.html">FAQ</A>, plus <A HREF="facts.html">facts you never knew</A> about RollerCoaster Tycoon. 
<P>

<FONT FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE="3" CLASS="3" COLOR="#0060FF"><B>PROBLEMS?</B></FONT><BR>
If you have problems with the game, check our <A HREF="support.html">Technical Support</A> areas.
<P>
If you have comments or questions about the CD-ROM, please check the FAQ.  If your question is not covered, please contact <a href="mailto:support@microprose.com?subject=RollerCoasterTycoon.com
Site">RollercoasterTycoon Support</a>.
<BR>
